    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a demo version of Tearscape, a 2D top-down action-adventure, blending fast-paced combat, exploration, and pixel art inspired by Game Boy Color classics. Fight monstrous foes, unlock new abilities, and explore a non-linear map filled with hidden secrets and dangerous challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you will have access to the tutorial area, the Graveyard, the forest, Hemlock Ward town, and the game's first two dungeons: Dreadmoor Palace and Hemlock Citadel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/718adccd946b86a062d2360b9cf92fbb.avif?t=1769683025\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/aed1e271eed69abf8bdc5e9b757fbc5e.poster.avif?t=1769683025\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/aed1e271eed69abf8bdc5e9b757fbc5e.webm?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/aed1e271eed69abf8bdc5e9b757fbc5e.mp4?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master precise combat, where every strike and dodge matters. Strategically manage your stamina by carefully considering each move as you face off against grotesque enemies. You have a limited number of healing flasks—use them wisely and plan your moments to recover carefully. Upgrade your character's stats to remain effective and competitive in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/a1479e615f1801db321abde8efb54139.avif?t=1769683025\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/3812afdac0aeb8b6f56dcf87679504d9.poster.avif?t=1769683025\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/3812afdac0aeb8b6f56dcf87679504d9.webm?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/3812afdac0aeb8b6f56dcf87679504d9.mp4?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you will explore the first two dungeons of the game: Dreadmoor Palace and Hemlock Citadel. They are packed with deadly traps and challenging enemies. Awaiting you at each  dungeon's end is a formidable boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/81c1b79c50f5e2e6606797dbdd6c617b.avif?t=1769683025\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65f373eb10ec92e5140fac6e795666f1.poster.avif?t=1769683025\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65f373eb10ec92e5140fac6e795666f1.webm?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65f373eb10ec92e5140fac6e795666f1.mp4?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you’ll challenge the game’s opening bosses: Seraph the Impure, a grotesque abomination of flesh and malice, and Nyxclaw, a majestic yet fearsome gryphon. With a combination of close and ranged attacks, they will test your skills. Beware of second phases, where unexpected and dangerous surprises await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/3f62c70ee32776ed167d124c7fbbe000.avif?t=1769683025\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65498780d92dbbe3440504bf2730b6b7.poster.avif?t=1769683025\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65498780d92dbbe3440504bf2730b6b7.webm?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/65498780d92dbbe3440504bf2730b6b7.mp4?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo, you'll explore the game's opening areas:  Graveyard, the forest, Hemlock Ward town and the first two dungeons: Dreadmoor Palace and Hemlock Citadel. The map is filled with branching paths and hidden shortcuts, so stay alert as you explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/50c8c61df36ecb909cab9bbb5111b637.avif?t=1769683025\" width=1560 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/4e5fd17e732897db0b45f6121e4a212c.poster.avif?t=1769683025\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/4e5fd17e732897db0b45f6121e4a212c.webm?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/4e5fd17e732897db0b45f6121e4a212c.mp4?t=1769683025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo introduces two NPCs: Valthor, who offers a small quest with a useful reward, and Aldric, your guide throughout the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
